- To create static library
  
  gcc -c prog1.c
  gcc -c prog2.c

Pack this libraries using:

  ar rcs libmylib.a prog1.c prog2.c 


You can see the contents of this library using

ar -t libmylib.a


- TO creta dynamic library


 gcc -c -fpic prog1.c
 gcc -c -fpic prog2.c


 gcc -shared -o libmylib.so prog1.o prog2.o
